    <h1>Proxy Demo</h1>
    <p>This demo shows the @astroscope/proxy package for HTTP proxying.</p>

    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>This page is handled by Astro</li>
      <li>Requests to <code>/api/*</code> are proxied to JSONPlaceholder API</li>
      <li>Any unmatched routes would fall through to a legacy backend (strangler fig pattern)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Try it</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/api/posts/1">GET /api/posts/1</a> - Proxied to JSONPlaceholder</li>
      <li><a href="/api/users/1">GET /api/users/1</a> - Proxied to JSONPlaceholder</li>
    </ul>
